data.description: *BACK ON-MARKET due to Buyer being unable to secure financing* This recently updated Bungalow style home features 2 bedrooms and 1 bathroom, with recent renovations that make this property truly stand out! Enjoy many years of home ownership and peace of mind that comes with having a newer roof, HVAC system, water heater, and electric panel! The kitchen has been updated with new cabinets, countertops, appliances, vinyl flooring installed throughout, remodeled bathroom, new fixtures & finishes, and freshly painted inside & out! With its vibrant arts scene, stunning beaches, and a wide range of recreational activities, St. Petersburg is a diverse and thriving community! Don't miss out on this rare opportunity - Contact us today to schedule your private showing!
